Module java.se

module java.se
Defines the API of the Java SE Platform.
Optional for the Java SE Platform:
Java Native Interface (JNI)
Java Virtual Machine Tool Interface (JVM TI)
Java Debug Wire Protocol (JDWP)
Since:
9
